  <primary_outcome>
    <measure>Ultrasound Biomicroscopy</measure>
    <time_frame>Up to 12 months</time_frame>
    <description>We will scan the cross section of the medial nerve at the pisiform bone level to determine the level of CTS with Ultrasound Biomicroscopy machine. This device is not approved for clinical decisions, only used for research purposes.</description>
  </primary_outcome>
